                            <comment id="14611" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Thu, 8 Sep 2005 06:06:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve refined ServletContextResourcePatternResolver to handle absolute paths returned by the servlet container as well. I haven&apos;t had a chance to test this on OC4J, though: Hence, please test one of the next nightly Spring snapshots and let me know whether it works for you!&lt;/p&gt;

